item.title: [317][PI]Need help fixing equip item speed!
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

Not really. Either remove the crap from the process() method, or queue the events in the output buffer, and send them all at once.

It looks like it’s either taking another cycle(600ms) to process. It’s not really a big deal though.
